o-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADt-m%E1%BB%99-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-l%E1%BA%A1c-phong-di%E1%BB%87c-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-rRYSphjANe-zNN-I1GaBaA">Nhật mộ (Nhật lạc phong diệc khởi) - 日暮（日落風亦起）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-c%E1%BB%95-ca/poem-SQLcZneUoty6Zn7UCfgM4Q">Thạch cổ ca - 石鼓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thai-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-di-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-QdADUUqIuccobnxI7pw9DA">Thai Dương di sự - 邰陽遺事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/Thi%C3%AAn-Quan-giang/poem-_BeccPVM3HGGrnQq91DzSA">Thiên Quan giang - 天關江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
